{"lemma":"أَدَمَة","slug":"أَدَمَة","root":"#.د.م","root_slug":"_-د-م","root_link":"/words/roots/_-د-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n441","n448","n449"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n441","headword_ar":"ادّمهُ","root":"Adm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^odiymN","text_ar":"تَاْدِيمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put much"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAm","text_ar":"اـِدَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seasoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n448","headword_ar":"اُدْمَةٌ","root":"Adm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state of mixing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mingling, together"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in familiar,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"social, intercourse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Lth, T, M, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumaA A^udomapN","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمَا اُدْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Between them two is a mixing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (Lth, T.) ―         -b2-  Also, (M, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adomN","text_ar":"اَدْمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Agreement:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"familiarity, sociableness, companionship,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"friendship."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA. [The meanings in this sentence are assigned in the S only to the latter word: in the TA, only to the former.]) ―         -b3-  And the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Relationship."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A means of access"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasiylapN","text_ar":"وَسِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Fr, T, S, M, K) to a thing, (Fr, T, S,) and to a person; (Fr, T;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adamapN","text_ar":"اَدَمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomatiY A_ilayoka","text_ar":"اُدْمَتِى اـِلَيْكَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is my means of access to thee."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, T.) ―         -b5-  And [hence,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A present which one takes with him in visiting a friend or a great man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"in Peraian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dasot A=wiyz","text_ar":"دَسْت ا=وِيز"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, L.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^udomapu","text_ar":"هُوَ اُدْمَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholihi","text_ar":"اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^udomapN lifulaAnK","text_ar":"هُوَ اُدْمَةٌ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adamapN","text_ar":"اَدَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  In camels,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A colour intermixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tinged, with blackness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with whiteness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clear whiteness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) or, as some say, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense whiteness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness, with blackness of the eyeballs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Nh, TA:) and in gazelles,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a colour intermixed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tinged, with whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or in gazelles and in camels,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) and in human beings, (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tawny colour;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness of complexion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumorapN","text_ar":"سُمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; (S, M, K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an intermixture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tinge, of blackness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sumorap","text_ar":"سُمْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tawniness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and it is said to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomapu AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"اُدْمَةُ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the colour of the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Nh, TA:) or [in men,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HumorapN","text_ar":"حُمْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which, in this case, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of complexion]: (TA:) accord. to AHn, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whiteness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayaADN","text_ar":"بَيَاضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=damu","text_ar":"ا=دَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","TA","Fr","T","Nh"]},{"entry_id":"n449","headword_ar":"اَدَمَةٌ","root":"Adm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomapN","text_ar":"اُدْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^adamapu A^aholihi","text_ar":"هُوَ اَدَمَةُ اَهْلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomatuhumo","text_ar":"اُدْمَتُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adomatuhumo","text_ar":"اَدْمَتُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomuhumo","text_ar":"اُدْمُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adomuhumo","text_ar":"اَدْمُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAmuhumo","text_ar":"اـِدَامُهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the pattern, exemplar, example,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of imitation, of his people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"family, by means of whom they are known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) so says IAar. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalotu fulaAnFA A^adamapa A^aholiY","text_ar":"جَعَلْتُ فُلَانًا اَدَمَةَ اَهْلِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made such a one to be the pattern, exemplar, example,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object of imitation, of my people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"family."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^adamapN lifulaAnK","text_ar":"هُوَ اَدَمَةٌ لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomapN","text_ar":"اُدْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is a pattern,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN A^adamapu baniY","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ اَدَمَةُ بَنِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is he who makes people to know the sons of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^adamapu qawomihi","text_ar":"هُوَ اَدَمَةُ قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"provost, of his people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomihi","text_ar":"قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN A_idaAmu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ اـِدَامُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banY A^abiyhi","text_ar":"بَنى اَبِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^udomu","text_ar":"اُدْمُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is the aider, and manager of the affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the support,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right orderer of the affairs, of his people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the sons of his father."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inner skin;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cutis,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"derma;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior of the skin, which is next to the flesh;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) the exterior thereof being called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba$arap","text_ar":"بَشَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or (as some say, M) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exterior thereof, upon which is the hair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the interior thereof being called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba$arap","text_ar":"بَشَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adamN","text_ar":"اَدَمٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be its pl.; [or rather, a coll. gen. n.;] or, accord. to Sb, it is a quasi-pl. n. (M.) ―         -b2-  Accord. to some, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What appears of the skin of the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba$arapN","text_ar":"بَشَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interior"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the earth or ground; (M, K;) the surface thereof being called its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adiym","text_ar":"اَدِيم"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, TA:) or, as some say, its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surface."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","TA"]}]}}